net.jhoogland.jautomata.semirings

Class KTropicalSemiring<K extends Comparable<K>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.jhoogland.jautomata.semirings.KTropicalSemiring<K>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Semiring<List<PathWeight<K>>>

    public class KTropicalSemiring<K extends Comparable<K>>
extends Object
implements Semiring<List<PathWeight<K>>>
    This semiring is used by the shortest distance algorithm to determine the n shortest distances to a state. If the storePath field has value true, then the paths are stored that led to the n shortest distances.\
    Author:
    Jasper Hoogland
